1
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,270
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:36,320
[Episode 17 A Blood Oath]

3
00:00:36,350 --> 00:00:38,400
[Dedication Above Self]

4
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:49,750
Two things.

5
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:52,430
First, Fengling has searched
the Zhao residence

6
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:54,030
but found nothing abnormal.

7
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,930
His family has been
farming for generations.

8
00:00:55,930 --> 00:00:59,250
The claim that the gold was passed down
is unreliable.

9
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:00,600
Second,

10
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:03,670
she also checked with several
large native banks.

11
00:01:03,670 --> 00:01:06,630
Gold ingots of this quality and shape

12
00:01:07,230 --> 00:01:08,710
in recent decades

13
00:01:08,730 --> 00:01:11,130
have not circulated in Yin-Yang Crossing.

14
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,510
If the gold

15
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:15,680
has no source,

16
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:19,210
did it appear under the pillow
out of thin air?

17
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,430
Lady Fufeng,

18
00:01:21,710 --> 00:01:22,680
look at this.

19
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,800
Mr. Wu

20
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:33,280
once ordered his apprentice
to clean the place.

21
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:36,080
And according to Zhao Er's testimony,

22
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,009
his mother

23
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:40,479
also cleaned the house

24
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,940
inside and out three days ago.

25
00:01:41,940 --> 00:01:43,250
It can be seen

26
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,490
that this cleaning

27
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:46,120
is not ordinary behavior.

28
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:48,200
After Wu Youdao cleaned,

29
00:01:48,220 --> 00:01:49,140
he got the gold,

30
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:50,039
killed someone,

31
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:50,789
and fled.

32
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:53,200
After Mrs. Zhao cleaned,

33
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,400
she gave the gold

34
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,530
and hanged herself.

35
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,560
This sounds like

36
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:00,870
life-buying money,

37
00:02:03,910 --> 00:02:05,570
either buying someone else's

38
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,480
or buying one's own.

39
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:11,030
Wu Youdao was strong enough to kill,

40
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:14,190
but Mrs. Zhao was too old and frail

41
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:15,820
and could only kill herself.

42
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:22,940
Lord Bai,

43
00:02:23,290 --> 00:02:24,480
before you came,

44
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,520
Yin-Yang Crossing had existed
for thousands of years.

45
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,920
Get a good night's sleep.

46
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:29,940
Tomorrow,

47
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:31,630
everything won't collapse.

48
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:33,310
Lady Fufeng, my body...

49
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:45,620
I really don't know whether

50
00:02:47,930 --> 00:02:49,060
it's a good decision

51
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,680
to allow you to stay here.

52
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,080
Wu Youdao,

53
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:09,630
come here.

54
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:18,430
Come on.

55
00:03:23,790 --> 00:03:24,440
Eat.

56
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:26,000
Take everything you want.

57
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,530
These are

58
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,520
what you deserve.

59
00:03:31,370 --> 00:03:32,300
You're destined

60
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:35,910
to connect with
the Fortune-Turning Master.

61
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:38,690
Your skill helped you pass the trial.

62
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,850
From now on,

63
00:03:46,770 --> 00:03:47,610
we

64
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:50,910
are all believers of
the Fortune-Turning Master.

65
00:03:51,210 --> 00:03:52,770
As long as you are obedient,

66
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,710
these are

67
00:03:54,610 --> 00:03:55,890
all yours.

68
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:59,000
He will bless you.

69
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,440
Lady Fufeng.

70
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,280
Master.

71
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:13,000
Wu Youdao hasn't been caught yet.

72
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,740
The guys are casting a wide net
to find him.

73
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:16,529
But there's something strange.

74
00:04:16,529 --> 00:04:18,290
The waiter from the tavern next door said

75
00:04:18,290 --> 00:04:19,610
that two days
before Wu Youdao disappeared,

76
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:21,209
while drinking at Zuiwang Tavern,

77
00:04:21,209 --> 00:04:22,930
he mysteriously talked
to a table of people

78
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:24,120
about

79
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:25,920
Fortune-Turning Master.

80
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,380
Yes.

81
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,660
I also found out

82
00:04:28,890 --> 00:04:30,780
that the day before Mrs. Zhao
hanged herself,

83
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:32,920
when chatting with neighbors
at the end of the alley,

84
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:35,450
she also mentioned Fortune-Turning Master.

85
00:04:36,260 --> 00:04:37,200
What did they say?

86
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,460
My Lord, you're awake.

87
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,320
How do you feel?

88
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,120
Tell me,

89
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:43,230
what's going on with
Fortune-Turning Master?

90
00:04:43,870 --> 00:04:44,680
Well...

91
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:48,280
Granny Wang, have you heard?

92
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:50,620
If by the roadside or in a corner,

93
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:53,159
you find a small stone
with a red talisman on it,

94
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:55,920
it means the Fortune-Turning Master
has his eye on you.

95
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,190
As long as you carry this stone with you,

96
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,920
he can help you solve all your problems.

97
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,160
Is that true?

98
00:05:07,220 --> 00:05:08,860
Fortune-Turning Master.

99
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,160
How could there be such a good thing?

100
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:15,050
Did you send someone to keep
an eye on the Zhao family?

101
00:05:15,050 --> 00:05:16,180
Anything abnormal?

102
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:18,560
I checked it myself.

103
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,090
This morning, under the pillows
of Zhao Er and his mother,

104
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:22,610
no new gold appeared.

105
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:23,870
Yes.

106
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,870
They are already dead.

107
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:27,910
How could there be more gold?

108
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:29,940
Cleaning,

109
00:05:29,970 --> 00:05:31,090
spreading rumors,

110
00:05:31,380 --> 00:05:32,690
and then killing,

111
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,159
they're interlocked.

112
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:39,920
It seems

113
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:42,640
someone wants to build
another Xiqianhua

114
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:44,630
in Yin-Yang Crossing.

115
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:48,800
This logic

116
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:51,890
is actually recruiting believers.

117
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,480
First,

118
00:05:53,590 --> 00:05:54,470
cleaning.

119
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,870
Through this seemingly ordinary behavior,

120
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,430
they can get rewards.

121
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,960
This is the beginning of faith.

122
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,840
Second,

123
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:02,270
spreading rumors.

124
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:04,950
Tell the rumors to more people

125
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,670
to draw more people on board.

126
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,000
Third,

127
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,240
killing.

128
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:11,460
This is the real oath of allegiance.

129
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:13,190
Those who commit murder

130
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:16,100
will definitely be pursued
by Xiqianhua and the authority.

131
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:18,700
They will become fugitives
with nowhere to go.

132
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,840
Then, they will wholeheartedly

133
00:06:21,170 --> 00:06:22,280
turn to this new master

134
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:25,010
who grants them sins and gold.

135
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:29,380
How dare he turn things upside down
in Yin-Yang Crossing?

136
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:29,980
Master,

137
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:31,890
I will take my men
to patrol the streets right now.

138
00:06:31,890 --> 00:06:33,830
If we find someone cleaning for no reason,

139
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,850
we will go in and keep an eye
on him immediately.

140
00:06:34,850 --> 00:06:35,530
No.

141
00:06:35,550 --> 00:06:36,480
Miss Fengling.

142
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:39,190
Cleaning seems unusual,
but it is an ordinary behavior.

143
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,920
If we act rashly,

144
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:43,530
it will only make the people
panic and complain,

145
00:06:43,530 --> 00:06:46,190
falling right into
the trap of this evil spirit.

146
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:55,920
My Lord, are you alright?

147
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:58,340
How could a cold cause you
to cough up blood?

148
00:06:58,930 --> 00:06:59,730
My Lord.

149
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:02,220
It's fine, Shuan.

150
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:03,480
Don't be afraid.

151
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,950
There's nothing to fuss about.

152
00:07:06,970 --> 00:07:09,100
The symptoms are just a bit more severe.

153
00:07:09,100 --> 00:07:11,270
Besides, Lady Fufeng
is sitting right here.

154
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,530
What are you afraid of?

155
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:15,860
I'm fine.

156
00:08:59,150 --> 00:08:59,940
My Lord.

157
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,290
My Lord.

158
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:03,520
I am sorry, My Lord.

159
00:09:04,370 --> 00:09:05,370
I have no choice.

160
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,520
I really have no choice, My Lord.

161
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,040
My Lord.

162
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,340
Shuan.

163
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,120
My Lord.

164
00:09:49,650 --> 00:09:51,290
My Lord.

165
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:52,630
I am sorry, My Lord.

166
00:09:52,650 --> 00:09:53,410
My Lord.

167
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,870
I didn't mean it, My Lord.

168
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:56,860
I couldn't control myself, My Lord.

169
00:09:56,860 --> 00:09:58,240
My Lord, please don't blame me.

170
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:58,930
My Lord.

171
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,910
Shuan.

172
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,170
Don't be afraid.

173
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,100
I am here.

174
00:10:12,570 --> 00:10:16,000
Three days ago, I went to the market
to buy groceries

175
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,190
and heard someone talking about

176
00:10:18,190 --> 00:10:19,650
Fortune-Turning Master.

177
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:21,640
It sounded so miraculous.

178
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,390
They said as long as you are sincere,

179
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:27,720
you can meet immortals
and solve all problems.

180
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:30,910
Is the Fortune-Turning Master
really effective?

181
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,000
Of course.

182
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:33,730
Madam Li next door told me.

183
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,410
It can't be fake.

184
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:40,990
Have you heard of
the Fortune-Turning Master?

185
00:10:41,330 --> 00:10:42,270
I heard that

186
00:10:42,430 --> 00:10:43,810
as long as you are sincere,

187
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:46,190
if you find a small stone
by the roadside or in a corner

188
00:10:46,190 --> 00:10:49,040
with a red talisman on it,

189
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:51,970
it means you have an affinity
with Fortune-Turning Master.

190
00:10:51,970 --> 00:10:54,430
As long as you keep this small stone
with you,

191
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,210
you can turn bad luck into good.

192
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:58,670
Fortune-Turning Master will guide you
in your dreams,

193
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:01,330
and even the biggest disasters
can be resolved.

194
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:02,750
Is it real?

195
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,240
Everyone says so.

196
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:05,960
Did you find one?

197
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:07,510
If I had found one,

198
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:08,760
I would have been rich by now.

199
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,280
That makes sense.

200
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,080
I... I was tempered

201
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,550
and picked it up.

202
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:26,790
It was this stone.

203
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,670
I brought it back.

204
00:11:29,090 --> 00:11:30,480
When I went to sleep at night,

205
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,550
I held it in my hand

206
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,300
and thought to myself.

207
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:37,080
I wish to pay off the debts
my parents owed

208
00:11:37,260 --> 00:11:39,000
our neighbors when they were alive.

209
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,800
I silently prayed to
the Fortune-Turning Master.

210
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,200
Shuan.

211
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:46,400
I've seen through your misfortune.

212
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:50,120
To get gold, you must sign
a spiritual pact.

213
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:53,000
Do one thing for me every day,

214
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:55,600
and I will reward you
with one piece of gold.

215
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,030
There are three taboos.

216
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:59,080
Keep them in mind.

217
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:01,800
Never tell a third person.

218
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,960
Never leave this stone.

219
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:06,790
Never regret this deal.

220
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:12,750
Violators will lose this bond
and their souls will vanish.

221
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,920
When I woke up in the morning,

222
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:16,960
I really saw a gold ingot

223
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,320
by my pillow.

224
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,200
And

225
00:12:19,830 --> 00:12:21,030
there was also a note.

226
00:12:21,170 --> 00:12:23,630
On the note was written,
"Clean your house."

227
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,070
I was terrified.

228
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:27,010
But I dare not disbelieve it,

229
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:28,360
or disobey the three taboos,

230
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,870
let alone tell anyone.

231
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,690
I just thought to myself

232
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,550
that cleaning isn't hard anyway,

233
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:35,080
so I might as well just do it.

234
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:37,150
The county yamen is my home.

235
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,240
I cleaned every place

236
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,610
I could.

237
00:12:41,290 --> 00:12:43,080
When I woke up the next day,

238
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:45,490
there was indeed another gold ingot.

239
00:12:45,650 --> 00:12:46,980
And a new note.

240
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,360
On the note was written,

241
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:52,610
" Tell others the story of
the Fortune-Turning Master."

242
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,480
I was terrified.

243
00:12:54,650 --> 00:12:55,170
But

244
00:12:55,410 --> 00:12:57,020
I was greedy for the gold.

245
00:12:58,150 --> 00:13:00,670
So when I went grocery
shopping in the morning,

246
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:02,930
I secretly told a few vegetable vendors.

247
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,400
Until just now,

248
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:07,560
I fell asleep and woke up startled，

249
00:13:07,580 --> 00:13:09,180
and the gold appeared again.

250
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,590
But this time,

251
00:13:14,060 --> 00:13:15,120
this time it was...

252
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:18,810
[Kill someone]

253
00:13:19,740 --> 00:13:20,900
This time...

254
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,720
So you took advantage of
Lord Bai's severe illness,

255
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,950
thinking he was an easy target,

256
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:35,280
and tried to kill him.

257
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:36,480
Shuan.

258
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:37,960
You know how kind Lord Bai

259
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,030
treats you.

260
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:40,880
Have you lost your conscience?

261
00:13:40,930 --> 00:13:42,180
Fortunately, Lord Bai was sharp

262
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:43,910
and remembered you cleaning vigorously.

263
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:44,570
Otherwise,

264
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,370
how could his frail body

265
00:13:46,390 --> 00:13:47,600
withstand your attack?

266
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,440
No.

267
00:13:48,470 --> 00:13:50,400
I didn't want to kill you, I didn't.

268
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,810
I just wanted to do as usual

269
00:13:51,810 --> 00:13:53,290
and tuck you in.

270
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:55,510
But the moment I got close,

271
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:57,110
my mind went blank.

272
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,330
A voice kept urging me.

273
00:14:00,530 --> 00:14:02,670
I don't know why I had
murderous thoughts either.

274
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,950
My Lord, I couldn't control myself!

275
00:14:04,970 --> 00:14:06,500
I couldn't control myself.

276
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,200
Get up.

277
00:14:18,970 --> 00:14:19,520
I'm fine.

278
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:21,030
The three taboos are wise.

279
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:23,060
Silence them,

280
00:14:23,090 --> 00:14:24,490
restrain their actions,

281
00:14:24,490 --> 00:14:25,890
and cut off their escape.

282
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:30,600
This evil spirit wants to sever
people's conscience and bonds

283
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,840
one by one,

284
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:34,160
turning them into puppets in its palm.

285
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:40,180
My Lord,

286
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,000
I've seen

287
00:14:42,130 --> 00:14:44,060
the patterns on this stone before.

288
00:14:52,190 --> 00:14:53,160
This talisman

289
00:14:53,890 --> 00:14:56,750
and the oiled paper talisman
at the flatbread stall

290
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,300
come from the same source.

291
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,270
Exactly.

292
00:15:01,370 --> 00:15:02,930
This is a spell to attract evil power.

293
00:15:02,930 --> 00:15:05,590
Carving it on a stone
makes its effect stronger.

294
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,790
It can continuously attract
trace amounts of evil power

295
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:09,590
without being easily detected.

296
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:13,000
It imperceptibly distorts
the wearer's mind,

297
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:16,790
amplifies greed, and bewitches them.

298
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:24,030
So, giving orders in dreams
and sending gold out of thin air

299
00:15:24,390 --> 00:15:26,120
are all tricks of this stone.

300
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:27,810
Have you forgotten

301
00:15:28,270 --> 00:15:31,270
how the mirror spirit was
trapped in the nightmare?

302
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,840
Bai Han is already used to this.

303
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:39,440
This stone is just
a new method he found.

304
00:15:39,810 --> 00:15:41,770
The so-called Fortune-Turning Master

305
00:15:41,770 --> 00:15:44,200
is clearly a Disaster-Bringing Master.

306
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,240
How many of these stones

307
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:49,000
have been scattered in Yin-Yang Crossing?

308
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:55,930
It's mine.

309
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:57,960
I took it. Listen to me.

310
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,440
Don't fight over it.

311
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,030
This is mine.

312
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:00,080
What are you doing? Give it to me.

313
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,030
Cleaning,

314
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,090
spreading rumors,

315
00:16:02,090 --> 00:16:02,850
and killing.

316
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,860
This matter might spread like wildfire

317
00:16:04,860 --> 00:16:06,590
and get completely out of hand.

318
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:09,550
My Lord.

319
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:10,960
My Lord, My Lady.

320
00:16:11,840 --> 00:16:12,600
Bad news!

321
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:14,120
There's a knife fight
at the East Market crossing!

322
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:14,980
What happened?

323
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,530
For a stone,

324
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:18,360
two obedient peddlers

325
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:20,400
both went crazy

326
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:21,770
over a stone with a red talisman.

327
00:16:21,770 --> 00:16:23,800
One peddler grabbed
a machete from his pole

328
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:25,110
and hacked the other.

329
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:26,930
Blood splattered everywhere.

330
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:27,840
My Lord.

331
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,480
Lady Fufeng.

332
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,480
Some cases happened this morning.

333
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,910
An unidentified corpse
was fished out of the river.

334
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:33,840
It has scars,

335
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:35,030
not like an accidental death.

336
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:36,720
An old beggar died
at the refugee settlement.

337
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:38,030
His head seems to have taken a heavy blow.

338
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,270
A family on West Street reported

339
00:16:39,270 --> 00:16:41,290
that their child fell into
a well and died.

340
00:16:41,290 --> 00:16:42,910
Moreover, their neighbor is missing.

341
00:16:42,910 --> 00:16:44,750
The causes and methods of death vary.

342
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:45,700
But I feel

343
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:47,200
that these cases are

344
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:49,530
related to that Fortune-Turning Master.

345
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:53,240
Evil spirits are confusing the public,
causing chaos.

346
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:55,500
We cannot let it spread any further.

347
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,000
Fengling,

348
00:16:57,300 --> 00:16:58,840
issue the highest ban immediately.

349
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,560
Tell all creatures in Yin-Yang Crossing
that spreading the heresy of

350
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:02,910
the Fortune-Turning Master
is strictly prohibited.

351
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:05,500
Everyone should not touch nor held stones
with talismans.

352
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,500
Violators will be

353
00:17:06,609 --> 00:17:10,540
treated as colluding with evil spirits
and will be punished severely.

354
00:17:10,589 --> 00:17:11,240
Hu.

355
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,810
Lead a team personally.

356
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:14,240
Spirit envoys are at your disposal.

357
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,480
Search the whole county today.

358
00:17:16,630 --> 00:17:17,880
Once seeing this evil stone

359
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,800
hand it in to Xiqianhua Mansion.

360
00:17:19,829 --> 00:17:20,339
Yes, ma'am.

361
00:17:20,339 --> 00:17:21,200
Wait.

362
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:27,430
Do you have any objections?

363
00:17:27,589 --> 00:17:28,400
My Lady.

364
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,350
This method is massive in scale,

365
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:32,160
which can indeed deter the scoundrels.

366
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,350
But it's just a temporary fix

367
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:35,480
and might even backfire.

368
00:17:36,820 --> 00:17:37,650
My Lord.

369
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,750
How could it backfire?

370
00:17:40,730 --> 00:17:41,960
That's human nature.

371
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:43,650
If you make a big fuss
about confiscating stones,

372
00:17:43,650 --> 00:17:45,330
not only will the people not be grateful,

373
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:46,950
but also they will become rebellious,

374
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:49,270
thinking that the county yamen
and Xiqianhua

375
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:51,130
are afraid of Fortune-Turning Master,

376
00:17:51,130 --> 00:17:52,920
and are therefore suppressing it.

377
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:56,780
This will further validate the legend
that the stone truly has power.

378
00:17:58,230 --> 00:17:59,470
That seems to be true.

379
00:18:03,630 --> 00:18:05,000
The most important thing right now

380
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,930
is not to destroy those few stones,

381
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:10,350
but to eliminate people's greed
and wishful thinking.

382
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,380
Do you have any solutions?

383
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,720
Yes.

384
00:18:18,110 --> 00:18:21,110
But the county magistrate, Hu,

385
00:18:21,130 --> 00:18:23,590
and Miss Fengling have to
make some efforts.

386
00:18:31,190 --> 00:18:32,600
You scoundrel!

387
00:18:33,230 --> 00:18:34,710
In public,

388
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:37,020
how dare you commit a crime with a knife!

389
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:38,870
Tell me.

390
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:42,920
Why did you kill the victim?

391
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:51,320
I didn't kill him.

392
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:54,350
I really didn't kill him.

393
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,590
It was the Fortune-Turning Master

394
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,510
who asked me to kill him.

395
00:18:58,690 --> 00:18:59,930
He gave me gold

396
00:19:00,050 --> 00:19:02,400
and told me,
"As long as you kill that man,

397
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:05,570
you will gain wealth."

398
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:09,440
It's the Fortune-Turning Master
spreading fallacies again.

399
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,290
Guys,

400
00:19:10,630 --> 00:19:11,360
search him.

401
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:19,880
It's mine! Mine!

402
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:20,960
This is mine!

403
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:25,920
Everyone, look closely.

404
00:19:26,270 --> 00:19:28,400
This is that Fortune-Turning Master.

405
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,530
Fortune-Turning Master, spare my life.

406
00:19:32,530 --> 00:19:34,190
I don't want the gold anymore.

407
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:35,580
Fortune-Turning Master, spare my life.

408
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:37,340
I don't want the gold anymore.

409
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,330
What the Fortune-Turning Master
gives people

410
00:19:45,330 --> 00:19:46,640
is never wealth.

411
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:50,410
He substitutes stones for gold

412
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:52,750
to lure people to commit crimes.

413
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:53,640
In the end,

414
00:19:53,770 --> 00:19:55,530
he devours your lives

415
00:19:55,850 --> 00:19:56,780
and souls.

416
00:19:57,270 --> 00:19:58,400
Did you all see that?

417
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:00,000
This thing claims lives.

418
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:03,000
Believing in it or spreading it

419
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:05,120
means your're killing yourselves.

420
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,140
My Lady.

421
00:20:11,660 --> 00:20:12,790
From today on,

422
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:16,250
people who have this stone on them
or in their homes

423
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:18,890
must hand it over to the county yamen
within one day.

424
00:20:18,890 --> 00:20:19,910
Thank you, My Lady.

425
00:20:19,910 --> 00:20:21,000
For those who voluntarily hand it over,

426
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,750
Xiqianhua will purify

427
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:25,030
the evil power they have
been infected with,

428
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:27,030
and past mistakes will be forgiven.

429
00:20:27,430 --> 00:20:29,430
We will obey the order of Xiqianhua.

430
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:32,400
Everyone, listen clearly.

431
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:34,030
Hand in the stones.

432
00:20:34,330 --> 00:20:35,520
Spread the news.

433
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:37,970
This is all for the sake
of your own lives.

434
00:20:38,210 --> 00:20:38,940
Yes, yes.

435
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:39,960
My Lord is right.

436
00:20:40,270 --> 00:20:41,400
We should hand it in.

437
00:20:41,510 --> 00:20:42,070
Yes.

438
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:59,640
Your plan has already worked.

439
00:21:01,150 --> 00:21:03,880
Right now, we need to strictly
guard these foul items

440
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:06,410
and destroy them
with spiritual power later.

441
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:10,350
Master, Lord Bai.

442
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:12,490
The preliminary interrogation is complete.

443
00:21:12,490 --> 00:21:14,430
Those who voluntarily
handed over gold today

444
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:17,230
had experiences similar
to what Shuan described.

445
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:20,720
Most people only followed
the evil spirit's instructions to clean

446
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,520
and did not progress to killing.

447
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:25,530
As for those three murders this morning,

448
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:27,630
I investigated them myself.

449
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:30,110
They were all man-made disasters,
not accidents.

450
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,910
It's not just these three cases.

451
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,080
Fengling.

452
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:36,150
Investigate the claims about
the Fortune-Turning Master.

453
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:39,420
Find out when, where, and from
whom they started.

454
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:41,030
I want the origin.

455
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,160
Yes.

456
00:21:44,630 --> 00:21:45,310
My Lady.

457
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:47,210
This matter is settled.

458
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:48,720
I'll return to the county yamen first

459
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:50,240
to sort today's clues.

460
00:21:52,030 --> 00:21:52,540
Wait.

461
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:05,510
My Lady.

462
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,240
Now,

463
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:10,440
I can no longer help restore
your spiritual power.

464
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,190
Or

465
00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:19,750
do you want to spend more time with me?
